{"tid":2250333,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「第四波」威爾斯周五起全面封鎖17日","createTime":"2020-10-20T04:49:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T06:23:19.000Z","uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a96e54af414be15795950a4678d2681467ef989d","tid":2250333,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:49:17.000Z","msg":"威爾斯地區周一宣佈周五傍晚6時起實施全面封鎖令，其間民眾必須留在家中，餐廳、酒吧及非必要商店將全面暫停營業，所有康樂事業、社區中心、圖書館將全面關閉，宗教場所除葬禮婚禮外不得舉行宗教儀式。威爾斯地區大學將持續提供部份個人及網上課程，若學生選擇留在學校，這段期間同樣建議待在宿舍中。與非同住者室內室外會面一律禁止，直到11月9日"},{"pid":"69bf198cd3d3ff48aed9f10d140ef87a770e676c","tid":2250333,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:53:02.000Z","msg":"會唔會有人唔夠糧食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d717ba1677189a62ccb23ecb9b4f69231d88d45","tid":2250333,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:59:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7042749d1c626f32074cb90b59ff97f0b3d2d8a7","tid":2250333,"uid":150466,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:00:28.000Z","msg":"眼殘以為沙田威爾斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8829980fb46db325749e4ba1506647b7ef0e3b","tid":2250333,"uid":138896,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7042749d1c626f32074cb90b59ff97f0b3d2d8a7","tid":2250333,"uid":150466,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:00:28.000Z","msg":"眼殘以為沙田威爾斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:06:20.000Z","msg":"嚇鬼死 睇標題都以為係PWH"},{"pid":"2c25f4c3f6913407a4c97695e3bdd50187fb6ccd","tid":2250333,"uid":79351,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7042749d1c626f32074cb90b59ff97f0b3d2d8a7","tid":2250333,"uid":150466,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:00:28.000Z","msg":"眼殘以為沙田威爾斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":